                            </p>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">Services Include</h3>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
